text: Anouska Helena Koster (born 20 August 1993) is a Dutch professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . Ahead of the 2021 season, Koster joined , forming part of the team's inaugural roster. ==Major results== ;2011 : 3rd Time trial, National Junior Road Championships ;2015 :1st Grand Prix Gippingen :1st 20px Young rider classification Energiewacht Tour :3rd Ronde van Overijssel ;2016 :1st 20px Road race, National Road Championships :1st 20px Young rider classification Ladies Tour of Qatar :3rd Overall Ladies Tour of Norway ::1st 20px Points classification ::1st Stage 3 :3rd Crescent Vårgårda Women World Cup TTT :3rd Drentse Acht van Westerveld ;2017 :1st 20px Overall Lotto Belisol Belgium Tour ::1st 20px Young rider classification ::1st Stage 3 :2nd Overall Gracia–Orlová ::1st 20px Points classification ::1st Stage 2 :2nd Road race, National Road Championships ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female cyclists Category:People from Dantumadiel Category:Sportspeople from Friesland
